Sinatra
    слушает сокет /tmp/procman-workers-status.socket
        {
            pid: 123,
            worker: 4,
            status: 3
        }
    шлет аяксом на страницу json
        [
            {
                pid: 124,
                workers: [
                    { worker: 8, status: 9 },
                    { worker: 9, status: 4 },
                    { worker: 10, status: 1 },
                ]
            }
        ]


Master Process
        слушает сокет /tmp/procman-master-porocess.socket
            {
                action: "new|stop|kill",
                pid: 32, # if stop or kill
                workers: 3 # if new
            }